      <title>亚洲公开赛形势喜忧参半；鲍威尔：市场休整导致国债下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰罗姆·鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)发表鹰派言论，导致标准普尔500指数连续第三次下跌，两年期国债收益率短暂触及5%，亚洲股市开盘涨跌不一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院将于周三举行波音双场听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/senate-to-host-dual-boeing-hearings-wednesday-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院将于周三举行两次听证会，调查波音公司的安全事故。彭博社的泰勒·肯德尔与领导调查的立法者讨论了预期的结果。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/senate-to-host-dual-boeing-hearings-wednesday-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:18:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
